data_test_aniso

# Synthetic CIF for v0.16.1 aniso parser verification.
# P1 cubic 4Å cell with two atoms (Ca at origin, O at body center) and
# explicit anisotropic displacement parameters in U-form (Å²). Diagonal
# Uᵢⱼ chosen to be visually distinct (Ca prolate along z, O isotropic).

_cell_length_a    4.0
_cell_length_b    4.0
_cell_length_c    4.0
_cell_angle_alpha 90.0
_cell_angle_beta  90.0
_cell_angle_gamma 90.0

loop_
_atom_site_label
_atom_site_type_symbol
_atom_site_fract_x
_atom_site_fract_y
_atom_site_fract_z
Ca1 Ca 0.0 0.0 0.0
O1  O  0.5 0.5 0.5

loop_
_atom_site_aniso_label
_atom_site_aniso_U_11
_atom_site_aniso_U_22
_atom_site_aniso_U_33
_atom_site_aniso_U_12
_atom_site_aniso_U_13
_atom_site_aniso_U_23
Ca1 0.012 0.012 0.030  0.000  0.000  0.000
O1  0.020 0.020 0.020  0.001 -0.002  0.003
